RT @MeghanEMorris: One dynamic I found fascinating as a @WeWork reporter: there hasn't been a rush of alumni startups, as with tech cos.

In this July piece, @srcasm helped me understand why + what he's seen from ex-WeWork founders: https://t.co/CbAb1chltQ https://t.co/lONUMHgtd0
